# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Data & binary artifacts — NEVER commit operational data to this public repo.
# This repo is code + documentation only. The patterns below are a safety net.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xlsm
*.xls
*.pbix
*.pbit
*.pptx
*.ppt
*.docx
*.html
*.htm
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.mp4
*.zip
*.eml

# Allow project config that happens to be JSON-based (kept intentionally)
!**/kpi_config.json

# Allow curated, sanitized report screenshots (identifiers redacted)
!**/screenshots/
!**/screenshots/*.png

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/
env/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS / editor
desktop.ini
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
